<p><span style="color: rgb(74, 37, 23); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); font-size: 24px;">经济管理学院组织员、党支部书记陈莹，党总支统战委员丁瑞凤，宣传委员杨磊，学生党支部组织委员黄山松，经济管理学院27期入党积极分子学班班长舒艳蒙作为评委，为选手打分。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(74, 37, 23); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELmic9EO5nw4PXNHiaMuibia5fYwyfdLwpABPZibwOgzDA4FrIMlqiaNVrWfTADIMPS05ZTiczmbN9Oic00Mg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="345" height="231" style="width: 345px; height: 231px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(74, 37, 23); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); vertical-align: inherit; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">比赛中，选手们紧扣红色主题，立足新时代要求，以铿锵有力的气势、饱满充沛的情感、声情并茂的演讲赢得在场同学们的阵阵掌声。</span></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 37, 23); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">第2组同学演讲的《跨越时空的井冈山精神》，引领我们穿越历史，一起回顾井冈山斗争的光辉历程，重温那段峥嵘岁月，感悟最真切和最强大的信仰力量；第5组同学演讲的《丰碑》，让我们彷佛看到了红军为革命事业而作出无私奉献的坚定信仰。</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span></p></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 37, 23); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 211); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>